---
import ServiceLayout from '../../components/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="NDIS Plan Reviews & Functional Capacity Assessments"
  description="NDIS plan review documentation and functional capacity assessments in Pakenham. Letters of support, OT reports, therapy plans and more."
  image="/images/services/ndis-reviews.jpg"
>
  <img src="/images/services/ndis-reviews.jpg" alt="NDIS documentation and functional capacity assessment" class="hero-image" />

  <h2>What to Expect</h2>
  <p>We are able to complete OT documentation required to help assist your NDIS plan review.</p>

  <p>Documents include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Letters of support</li>
    <li>NDIS OT Plan Review Reports</li>
    <li>Functional Capacity Assessment Reports</li>
    <li>NDIS OT Therapy Plans</li>
  </ul>

  <p>If you are a current client and are requiring OT documentation, please reach out to your clinician. If you are a new client and require OT documentation, please click the enquire button and complete an enquiry form.</p>
</ServiceLayout>
